&lt;p&gt;Sub-200ms latency is now achievable through modern neural architectures, and zero-shot voice cloning from 3-15 seconds of audio has become a standard feature set rather than premium.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Top 27 TTS AI Models by ELO&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;top-27-tts-ai-models-by-elo&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#top-27-tts-ai-models-by-elo&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

    
    &lt;div style=&#34;position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;&#34;&gt;
